responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "9B909B494A30B8E35ACB1EB488157DC9", "Oh good! The way I see it, we\'ll never clear those interlopers out while they\'re comfortable in their harborage. Someone needs to go smash up their nests. Do a good job of it, will you? Any leftovers just get repurposed into roadblocks when the highwaymen get a hold of \'em. So smash up anything you find really well. Don\'t leave them anything to come back to!")
name: 0006_P0_Tank2_54
